<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Opening SIUFIT...</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0; 
            padding: 0; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center; 
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #020617; 
            color: #FFFFFF; 
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #0F172A;
            border: 1px solid #1E293B;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 85%;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        h2 { 
            margin: 0 0 12px 0; 
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        p { 
            color: #94A3B8; 
            font-size: 15px; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6, #8B5CF6);
            color: white; 
            padding: 16px 32px; 
            border-radius: 100px;
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }
        #fallback {
            display: none; 
            margin-top: 24px; 
            padding: 16px;
            background-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #FCA5A5;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Opening SIUFIT 🚀</h2>
        <p>Your AI Coach is ready. If the app doesn't open automatically, tap the button below.</p>
        
        <a href="siufit://home" class="btn">Open App Now</a>

        <div id="fallback">
            <strong>App not installed?</strong><br>
            Please install the SIUFIT APK manually on your Android device to continue.
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        window.onload = function() {
            // 1. Automatically attempt to trigger the Android Deep Link
            setTimeout(function() {
                window.location.href = "siufit://home";
            }, 300);

            // 2. If the user is still looking at this webpage after 2.5 seconds, 
            // it means the app didn't open (likely not installed). Show the fallback message.
            setTimeout(function() {
                document.getElementById('fallback').style.display = 'block';
            }, 2500);
        };
    </script>
</body>
</html>
